Medford City Council, Mayor Lungo, and concerned members of the Medford community, on behalf of more than 275 emergency medical services professionals represented by Teamsters Local 25, who have proudly served the City of Medford through Armstrong Ambulance for more than 30 years, we write to express our strong support for Armstrong Ambulance and to urge

484
00:58:23,448 --> 00:58:32,172
