485
00:58:32,813 --> 00:58:48,821
For decades, Armstrong Ambulance has provided MedFed with reliable, high quality emergency medical services distinguished by strong clinical performance, operational consistency, and deep institutional knowledge of the community's need.

486
00:58:50,065 --> 00:58:55,870
Their record is well established and their workforce is experienced, professional and committed to public safety.

487
00:58:56,850 --> 00:59:11,582
At no point has the city identified any failure to any failure in clinical care, response, performance or operational capability that would justify removal of Armstrong as Medford EMS provider.

488
00:59:13,744 --> 00:59:32,609
