500
01:01:36,145 --> 01:01:40,048
The decision to replace a longstanding unionized EMS provider

501
01:01:40,548 --> 01:01:54,559
with a non-union company raises legitimate questions about whether labor considerations rather than service quality, workforce stability, or public safety played an improper role in the city's decision-making process.

502
01:01:55,319 --> 01:02:05,387
