507
01:03:04,615 --> 01:03:18,120
or labor representation, and engage in good faith negotiations with Armstrong Ambulance and Teamsters Local 25 to preserve jobs, protect public safety, and restore the community's trust.

508
01:03:18,760 --> 01:03:31,365
