Me and a lot of my co-workers, we're not gonna move to Cataldo in order to continue working in Bedford.

1075
01:47:12,987 --> 01:47:22,028
As much as we love this place, as much as we are passionate about serving this city, because of the company culture over there, because of a lot of different factors, because of all sorts of things.

1076
01:47:22,889 --> 01:47:28,810
It's kind of known that the cities at Cataldo services experience

1077
01:47:30,296 --> 01:47:30,997
longer response times.

1078
01:47:31,017 --> 01:47:34,559
There's been a lot made of response times tonight, and I'm sure there's a lot of numbers out there.

1079
01:47:35,200 --> 01:47:37,702
But I can only share my own personal experience.

1080
01:47:38,402 --> 01:47:56,716
In the summer of 2023, I was a supervisor for Armstrong's responding into the city of Everett, a city we do not service, with another one of our ambulances from Saugus, where firefighters had been on scene working a cardiac arrest in the first responders level, which is not the full scope of practice for a cardiac arrest, for 25 minutes.

1081
01:47:58,083 --> 01:48:00,886
on a young man who unfortunately did not make it.

1082
01:48:02,387 --> 01:48:15,298
And I cannot say whether it was a contributing factor, but just like Rich said, every minute of a cardiac arrest, that you are not getting high quality CPR in the way you're supposed to, decreases your survival chance by about 10%.

1083
01:48:17,675 --> 01:48:25,620
I hear stories time and time and time again of people who have had bad experience with Consolidate because of long response times, because they are stretched thin, they are short-staffed.

1084
01:48:26,901 --> 01:48:28,221
Private EMS is a very small world.

1085
01:48:28,402 --> 01:48:39,428
We've heard from a lot of our co-workers that are at Consolidate that people are not giving up their shifts to come to Medford, that Consolidate is counting on an influx of employees from Armstrong to staff those ambulances that they promised you in that contract.

1086
01:48:40,309 --> 01:48:40,949
That's not happening.

1087
01:48:44,027 --> 01:48:45,570
Like I said, I love working here.

1088
01:48:45,850 --> 01:48:48,295
I know the people of the city incredibly well.

1089
01:48:48,315 --> 01:48:49,677
I've worked here for a long, long time.

1090
01:48:51,180 --> 01:48:54,787
Knowing your patient population, knowing the patient, the city that you're serving.

1091
01:48:55,778 --> 01:48:56,278
is important.

1092
01:48:56,298 --> 01:48:57,579
That does not happen overnight.

1093
01:48:57,619 --> 01:48:59,339
That does not happen with a contract transfer.

1094
01:48:59,359 --> 01:49:05,502
That happens with people being in the city for a long period of time and caring for a long period of time.

1095
01:49:05,622 --> 01:49:08,923
And I certainly hope that I think sunlight is the best disinfectant.

1096
01:49:09,583 --> 01:49:12,064
If there are issues with Armstrong, I think they should be aired.

1097
01:49:12,084 --> 01:49:13,424
I think the chief should talk about it.

1098
01:49:13,444 --> 01:49:18,586
I think the chief of staff should be open and honest about it because I think the people of Medford deserve to know what those issues are.

1099
01:49:18,626 --> 01:49:19,907
I'm not saying that Armstrong is perfect.

1100
01:49:21,926 --> 01:49:25,008
I understand the situation that they're talking about with the longer response times.

1101
01:49:25,269 --> 01:49:30,832
But I also understand that Armstrong is willing to work with Medford in order to fix those issues.

1102
01:49:31,332 --> 01:49:35,014
And I don't think those issues are better served with it, although I think they're actually exacerbated.

1103
01:49:35,955 --> 01:49:42,479
So I don't know what the process is from here, but I certainly hope that there is some way that that can be examined.

1104
01:49:42,879 --> 01:49:43,139
Thanks.

1105
01:49:43,560 --> 01:49:46,101
And I appreciate your service to the Senate.

1106
01:49:46,161 --> 01:49:46,542
Thank you.

1107
01:49:46,562 --> 01:49:47,182
I appreciate it.

1108
01:49:50,673 --> 01:49:55,094
