1109
01:49:55,454 --> 01:49:56,495
I just want to let everybody know.

1110
01:49:56,695 --> 01:49:57,395
Thank you.

1111
01:49:58,215 --> 01:49:58,575
Floor is yours.

1112
01:49:58,595 --> 01:50:01,056
