1113
01:50:01,416 --> 01:50:01,696
Thank you.

1114
01:50:02,356 --> 01:50:03,436
My name is James Friederborn.

1115
01:50:03,676 --> 01:50:05,437
I live at 60 Elm Street in Medford.

1116
01:50:05,457 --> 01:50:07,677
I'm a Medford resident and a constituent of yours.

1117
01:50:08,257 --> 01:50:09,198
I'm also a paramedic.

1118
01:50:09,578 --> 01:50:12,678
I've worked as an EMT and paramedic in the Commonwealth for 12 years.

1119
01:50:13,099 --> 01:50:14,399
I do not work for Armstrong.

1120
01:50:14,419 --> 01:50:19,220
I've never worked for Armstrong, but I've worked for a various number of cities throughout the state and the country.

1121
01:50:20,061 --> 01:50:25,628
I've heard a lot of people here today say, you know, Talbot this, Armstrong that.

1122
01:50:25,908 --> 01:50:28,231
At the end of the day, they're both private companies.

1123
01:50:28,591 --> 01:50:29,592
They both work for pay.

1124
01:50:29,893 --> 01:50:31,194
They're both going to have their issues.

1125
01:50:31,935 --> 01:50:36,921
But what upsets me so much is that this is a company that has been here for 25 years.

1126
01:50:38,503 --> 01:50:42,708
Some of their medics and EMTs have served this community for so long.

1127
01:50:43,109 --> 01:50:53,321
And to see a decision made without public transparency, you know, I keep hearing, you know, 45 minute, you know, 45 minute this, you know, poor performance this, poor performance that.

1128
01:50:55,074 --> 01:50:56,755
I would like to see some transparency.

1129
01:50:57,415 --> 01:50:59,436
Clearly, the public is upset.

1130
01:51:00,156 --> 01:51:02,937
And I hear your frustrations, Chief, both of you.

1131
01:51:02,977 --> 01:51:05,398
I mean, you're both very well-respected, obviously.

1132
01:51:05,438 --> 01:51:10,020
I don't think that you don't know how to do your jobs.

1133
01:51:10,080 --> 01:51:14,562
But at the end of the day, it's about public transparency.

1134
01:51:15,062 --> 01:51:17,723
Clearly, there are people in Medford who are upset about this.

1135
01:51:18,636 --> 01:51:22,419
There needs to be more transparency on why this change occurred.

1136
01:51:23,060 --> 01:51:30,246
And honestly, at the end of the day, I think it's about standing up for our EMTs and paramedics who have served this community for 25 years.

1137
01:51:30,947 --> 01:51:35,131
I mean, I've heard, you know, we heard the chief of staff come up here and say, I could never do that job.

1138
01:51:35,511 --> 01:51:43,338
